fields.description:
Samsung always lead everyone with Galaxy Note series and now new number 9 is on its way with hell of looks which are beyond your thoughts that what they are going to do with all other brands like Huawei and LG.

Next in line Samsung Galaxy Note 9 leaked for too much time. Now its design is also revealed showing that bezels on the sides are almost gone while the legendary edge on sides of Samsung's Galaxy Note 9 is mesmerising but still you will get some looks of Note 8 in this phone. Stylus Pen is coming with more colour options as compare to previous phone.

Samsung Galaxy Note's launch is getting closer and it is speculated that this time they will launch it earlier as compare to past year. Galaxy S9 and S9 Plus hit the shelves but now a new beast Galaxy Note 9 by Samsung is going to add more fun in smartphone world because of its next generation technology.

I am talking about the Under screen fingerprint scanner which Samsung Galaxy's Note 9 is going to get for itself. It was speculated that devices from 2017 will have this technology but skipped due to uncertain reasons but now Samsung Note 9 acquired it for itself. 6.4 inch screen made up of Super AMOLED material got QHD Plus resolution.

Bixby is also improved and now it got 2.0 version for Galaxy Note 9. Face scanning is improved with more accuracy in judging faces to unlock the device. 4000 mAh battery is slightly bigger then its predecessor. Dual camera of Note 9 is consist of 12 MP primary sensor where the front camera is 8 MP. Camera sensor is improved to enhance the quality of images taken at night.

fields.description:
Samsung Galaxy S9 Plus 128GB - Expand Your Limits! Samsung is expanding limits of Galaxy S9 and now new variant named Plus 128GB is introduced with larger built-in storage which is going to accommodate lots of data.

So if you have trouble regarding your storage limit then Samsung Galaxy S9 Plus 128GB is a better choice for you to over come problem. With such vast storage still it has acquired additional SD card slot to expand storage of Samsung's Galaxy S9 Plus 128GB up to 256 via secure data card.

A true flagship device equipped with almost everything in it which an ordinary user need in its life and you can say that Samsung S9 Plus 128GB is true marvel of this decade due to its stunning design and specifications.

On both front and back side Corning Gorilla Glass 5 is used on Galaxy S9 Plus 128GB by Samsung which is going to cover the outer layer from scratches and dunt. IP68 certification is going to save the smartphone from dust particles whereas Samsung Galaxy S9's seal will protect the smartphone from seepage of water and you can keep your phone under water for almost thirty minutes up to the depth of 1.5 meters.

Samsung Galaxy's S9 Plus 128GB is going to inherit the Super AMOLED display which is home grown product of this brand where the size of screen is 5.8 inches. Due to its infinity nature Galaxy S9 Plus 128GB got resolution of 1440 x 2960 pixels and display is HDR 10 compliant too.

Always on Display is new feature which will tell you notifications and time on screen of S9 Plus 128GB even when screen of smartphone was not active. Android Oreo OS is going act as the mind of the smartphone.

fields.description:
Huawei P20 Pro - Setting New Trends For Photography!

Huawei Introduced another variant named P20 Pro which is professional version of its upcoming flagship devices. This time they bring huge change in the camera setup of smartphone where instead of single or dual lens Huawei P20 Pro acquired triple lens on its back.

In the setup of three first one is 40 MP main sensor second in command is 20 MP monochrome sensor while last sensor of Huawei's P20 Pro is 8 MP telephoto lens to truly capture the depth of images and give you the bokeh effect in the background of the main images.

In the give setup it seems that Huawei P20 Pro's main camera is going to come with f/1.8 aperture while the remaining is going to use the same old aperture that we often saw in all other devices. It seems odd that front side of P20 Pro by Huawei having only single camera which is consist of 24 MP lens. On the top front side you will see the difference in the screen of the smartphone where Huawei Pro is going to carry a Notch just like Apple iPhone X.

This company has reduced the bezels to minimum just like the Samsung but still they did not achieved what Korean giant has achieved. Huawei P20 Pro has stretched its corners to minimum and in that manner fingerprint sensor has to move back but still present on front side which mean that face unlock is seems missing in Huawei P20's Pro or you will get the both type of security protocols in this smartphone. Screen size of the device is 6.1 inches carrying trendy Full Vision screen where P20 Pro's resolution is 1080 x 2240 pixels. Well in the end power section of the device is equipped with massive 4000 mAh battery.

fields.description:
Vivo V9 - Mid-Ranger With Flagship Standards!

This brand Vivo surprisingly launched V9 with few modifications as compare to its predecessor. Rumor mill is active and ahead of its launch its first teaser image appeared and Vivo V9 is showed with a Notch on its top side.

It seems that this Notch style is quite trendy feature in Chinese market so each and every brand is going to make sure that they have Notch in its devices. V9 is one of them who followed this trend which was settle by the Apple for first time.

Samsung has some other planes and they are going to provide Vivo's V9 AMOLED panels to make the display better by producing deep black color. Display panel is trapped inside the 6.3 inch diagonal which has 1080 x 2280 pixel resolution. Vivo V9's pixels density will be 400 pixels per inch which mean that there will be better output due abundance of the pixels in per inch area.

After the display of Vivo grown V9 now it is time look inside the belly to check that we are going to find out in this phone. Qualcomm Snapdragon 626 chip is used as the basic platform on which you will get octa core processor that Vivo used in all of its devices and now V9 is going to get the same processor but here clock speed of the processor is dived into two categories where first four have a clock speed of 2.2 GHz while remaining four units of V9 have 1.8 GHz clock speed.

Adreno GPU is going to tackle the intense gaming while 4 GB of RAM is hired to maintain the multi-tasking of the V9 with special care. 64 GB of internal storage is located inside but it is backed up by 256 GB of SD card that will expand the storage according to your needs.

USB port of V9 by Vivo has an OTG support that make this phone capable to read your USB data too. 16 MP + 5 MP back camera has laser autofocus and LED flash while on the front side of Vivo V9 you will get the 24 MP cam with soft light flash.

fields.description:
OPPO Find X - Edge To Edge Screen With Pop Up Selfie Cam!

OPPO has finally launched its Find X smart device globally with some awesome features to confront all of its rivals with head to head. OPPO Find 7 was the last flagship from this series but now OPPO Find X pop up as the next generation phone to compete in market where its rival is also introducing new ways to capture the market but to overcome this kind of trouble.

OPPO Find X's manufacturer has decided to get edge over its competitors and that's why they are launching such kind of smartphone with pop up selfie camera that comes out from the top of OPPO's Find X. In the beginning it was not clear that what kind of display is going to come in this phone but now it is perfectly clear that AMOLED panel of 6.42 inches is installed on Find X's front side with a resolution of 1080 x 2340 pixels and if we talk about the ratio of the display then aspect ratio will be 19.5:9 because Notch is absent from top side of Find X by OPPO.

The display panels are imported from Samsung which mean that brightness and contrast of the display is going to look great where the video quality of the OPPO X is also going to improve a lot due to its enhanced display. Qualcomm Snapdragon 845 chipset has the duty to keep each and everything working and it also made OPPO Find's X a flagship phone.

Marvelous 8 GB of RAM is going to do the multi-tasking while 256 GB of built-in storage is truly amazing amount to store all kind of data inside OPPO Find X. Trendy feature Face ID is also added in package.

fields.description:
Samsung Galaxy S9 Plus - Leader Of Mobile Industry!

Samsung fans getting excited about Galaxy S9 but they don't know that Plus version is also coming to make it more excited for the lovers of this brand. S8 was the celebrity of the last year but the upcoming siblings are even better.

Samsung Galaxy S9 Plus got aluminum frame on its side while the front and back is covered with solid and thick layer of Corning Gorilla Glass 5 to make it scratch proof and save Samsung's Galaxy S9 Plus from shattering. This device also got an IP68 certificate which means that this smartphone can stay underwater for almost 30 minutes.

Samsung Galaxy S9's design is quite alike to this version but there is a difference between the display sizes of both devices. This phone is coming with massive 6.2 inch touchscreen. Galaxy S9 Plus by Samsung got the taste of Super AMOLED display which is exclusively made for the devices of this brand. Infinity screen is key selling point of these devices that's why Samsung S9 Plus is also coming with that kind of setup where the resolution will be 1440 x 2960 and pixel density reached the mark of 531.

Always on display is also present on the board of Galaxy S9 Plus that will keep you updated about the notifications. Next generation Snapdragon 845 chipset got the approval to come in these devices while Oreo is decorating the interior of S9 Plus.

Dual camera with 12 MP sensor is placed on the back side while for the front you will see the 8 MP selfie snapper in action. 6 GB of RAM is handling Samsung Galaxy's S9 Plus multi-tasking where internal storage of this device is 128 GB to handle all the storage needs.

Samsung Galaxy S9 - The Camera. Reimagined!

Samsung is shining star and Galaxy S9 will be the next premium device which is on its way. S8 is still in action and scoring huge amount of profit for the company but things have to move on and Samsung Galaxy S9 will be the next flagship device that we are see in the 2018.

No matter what happened in the past they improvised a lot and gained the trust of their user. Samsung's Galaxy S9 is expected to be just like its predecessor and and there will be not a bigger change in the design of the device. Still it is expected that Samsung Galaxy S9's specifications will be improved as compare to its previous model.

First thing which is revealed by the source is its chipset which is now improved and this chip of Galaxy S9 by Samsung will be built on 7nm chip but according to the news the Korean giant is not manufacturing chipset by its own because they are going to make 8nm chip this year.

Galaxy S9's Super AMOLED display is is key feature of the this company and in this device they are going to continue this trend and same edges will be seen in the Samsung S9 just like S8. Octa-Core processor is fitted on top of the chipset that will bring you improved user experience as compare to the previous version.

Newly born Samsung Galaxy's S9 is going to pack the Snapdragon 840 chipset which is going to be the most powerful and energy saving chip at this time. Android operating system v8.0 oreo is running Samsung Galaxy S9 inside the which is the most stable version of the Android with many improved tweaks.

Huawei P10 Plus - Unusual Offer!

Huawei appeared again with latest P10 Plus and now they have keep in mind the amazing success they have gain from their previous devices. Now company is thinking about launch and manufacturing of Huawei P10 Plus. At the same time they respects all their competitors and this is the quality of recognized leader.

The hero of our story is fresh to the news and we can say that Huawei's P10 Plus is really a gate to the new chapter of achievements for this leading Chinese brand. However, the price of new items is higher so that's why you have to pay extra money to get P10 Plus by Huawei in your hands.

From a design standpoint, it is a unique one as compare to other brands but it looks same to its younger brother. We can say that the Huawei P10 Plus's design has the originality that this company is renowned for. There is a metal case surrounding the display frame and a fingerprint reader is also there.

The screen of Huawei Plus is even more diagonal that is equals to 5.5 inches that one-handed person can easily use this gadget. IPS NEO LCD 1440 x 2560 pixel resolution of the device and LCD panel of Huawei P10's Plus puts together a good sharpness and highest levels of brightness and contrast. The main advantage is its Hi-Silicon Kirin 960 chipset that definitely worth to mention and record. Huawei P10 Plus has packed 6 GB RAM and 256 GB of ROM, which is sufficient for the majority of today's users.

Dual 20 MP + 12 MP and 8 megapixel camera for better image quality is close to many flagship solutions. P10 Plus's specifications deserves over payment only if you're a gamer or have even more impressive palms

Huawei Mate 10 Pro - Professionals Will Get Taste Of Oreo!

Huawei revealed the specifications of Mate 10 but another smartphone dubbed as Pro is on its way. Specifications have revealed that it will be the professional version of the basic device. Leaked specifications of upcoming Huawei Mate 10 Pro also affirmed that this phone is bringing updates and modifications too.

This phone is coming out of box with the Oreo operating system which is now available for everyone but Huawei's Mate 10 Pro will be the first one to get it. Chinese brand started to crack the code and use it for the next best device which is going to launch in upcoming days all across the globe.

Huawei Mate 10's Lite 18:9 ratio display is also present in gadget and now it became trendy for the flagships devices to carry it for themselves. Other specifications of Mate 10 Pro by Huawei includes 6.0 inch AMOLED capacitive LCD and on top of touchscreen is embedded for the firm and smooth touch.

Resolution provided inside the display of Huawei Mate's 10 Pro is 1080 x 2160 which is best display setup of this regarding to the smartphone world. 6 GB of RAM is expected to come packed which is going to take care of Huawei 10 Pro and its complex multi-tasking.

It is also speculated that Kirin 970 chipset will be used which is the most advance technology form this brand yet. Users of Mate 10 Pro will not face any kind of trouble with the storage because this phone is going to carry a 64 GB of internal storage and it is also speculated that 128 GB version of 10 Pro is also on its way to the leading markets of the world which is going to cause serious problem for Samsung.

OPPO F7 128GB - Click Pictures With Sensible Camera!

OPPO changing its strategy and F7 128GB is part of their new strategy in which they are going to launch each of their phone with a change in memory department and in that case OPPO F7 128GB is going to launch just on the same day as the basic version of this phone will be revealed.

So if your interested in this smart device and willing to get some extra memory then OPPO's F7 128GB will be your best buddy for as long as you want him in your life. 128 GB of internal storage will be coming in this new variant where dedicated slot for SD card is also present in F7 128GB's SIM slot try that will help you to increase your storage up to 256 GB and still you can use the other SIM slots for different networks at the same time.

OPPO F7 128GB's adapted to this approach to attract those who love to have some extra memory and before that Samsung used this approach too but now other players like F7 128GB by OPPO entered the competition too and to confront situation of hard competition this brand has decided to appear in market with total of three devices and one variant of OPPO 128GB will be named as the Youth variant of this phone.

This new phone is going to launch in Solar Red and Diamond Black colors where both of these colors of OPPO F7's 128GB will depict the true beauty of the device. Artificial Intelligence is upgraded to 2.0 version which is going to monitor the photography of 16 MP back and 25 MP front camera of OPPO F7 128GB. This new AI technology is going toughen the competition with Huawei.

Nokia 7 Plus - Design-led, style-forward most useful luxury accessory!

Nokia seems pretty mysterious about 7 Plus launch. We got our hands on some solid news that a new smartphone is going to reveal by the HMD Global Oy and it will be called Nokia 7 Plus. It seems that this device fits perfectly in the given scenario where on one side we have a mid-ranger and on the other side we have flagship device and specifications of Nokia's 7 Plus are showing that it will be the bridge between these two corners with not too high nor less specs.

In the GeekBench listing it is revealed that the Nokia 7 Plus's chipset will be made by the leading vendor Qualcomm and the model of the chipset will be Snapdragon 660 which is little better then the SD 630 that was used in the predecessor of 7 Plus by Nokia. We were expecting 6 GB of RAM but instead of our expectations we have got 4 GB of RAM that will be a perfect weapon against the messy multi-tasking of Nokia Plus.

In the past days Samsung was not too much famous as this brand was but now once again we will see that it will rise again as the star of the galaxy and Nokia 7's Plus is going to take one step closer to its victory.

Internal storage seems to be same as we got in previous device which was 64 GB and it will be backed up the SD card that gonna use the 7 Plus's second SIM slot. Oreo operating system is going to come out of the box because this brand did not add any spicy user interface so you are going to enjoy pure android in Nokia 7 Plus.

Xiaomi Mi 8 - Celebrating 8th Anniversary!

Xiaomi is going to celebrate Mi 8 launch in upcoming few days and with that they will also celebrate their 8th anniversary in which they have achieved too many goals and you can say that Xiaomi Mi 8 is big achievement too because this phone is true face of the now days flagship.

Under display fingerprint is the main attraction of this smartphone and Xiaomi Mi 8's Qualcomm Snapdragon 845 chipset is what makes him the flagship of this era. As we all know that Xiaomi Mi 7 was the next in line according to the company's plane but Xiaomi's Mi 8 is the finalized name of that device to which we know with an other name and reason behind this is also solid that its time to celebrate their birthday and there should be a solid device like Mi 8 by Xiaomi who is worthy smartphone to celebrate this event.

Samsung and Huawei are still doing their best to deliver under display fingerprint scanner but Xiaomi 8 has already got this unique tech fro itself. As far its specifications are concerned you will get the 6.21 inch of a massive LCD made up of IPS panels that gave Xiaomi Mi's 8 high definition resolution of 1080 x 2248 pixels.

Display is trapped inside the stainless steel frame where back and front side is covered with glass to give the Xiaomi Mi 8 a glossy look. Android OS v8.1 Oreo is going to be act as the brain of the smartphone where MIUI 9 is going to mask the software with its stunning looks. 6 GB RAM is attached with the Mi 8's chipset while internal storage of the smartphone is 64 GB only.

Infinix Zero 5 - Stay True!

Infinix planted another seed named Zero 5 which is going to be a mind blowing gadget and it is also the flagship device of company which is going to launch in Dubai with a glory of king. Infinix Zero 5 is speculated to be a bearer of unibody metal design just like Samsung carved from one single piece of metal which is going to look great on the slim and shiny body of the Infinix's Zero 5.

Other leaked details showing that this phone is going to carry a massive 6 GB of RAM which is now confirmed. 12 MP camera is equipped with Sony IMX3866P Lens and it seems that Infinix Zero 5's chip is capable to support such type of camera on its back where 13 MP telephoto lens is also present on back to accompany back camera.

Zero 5 by Infinix is equipped with 5.98 inches mammoth display that brought you better viewing angles and resolution is upgraded to FHD which mean that now you will be able to watch things in 1080 x 1290 pixels.

Infinix 5 is capable to do a lot other things and if we enlist them then on top of list we will meet the amazing 16 MP camera on its front side that makes Zero 5's camera able to take the high quality pictures and videos with the fine resolution of pixels. Front camera also carry bokeh effect so you can blur the background of images.

Internal storage of Infinix Zero's 5 is 64 GB which is used to store memorable pictures. Recently launched Android OS v7.0 Nougat is topped with XOS 3.0 that running through the veins of Infinix Zero 5 that makes sure that every thing run according to plane.

fields.description:
Apple iPhone X - 10th Anniversary Gift!

Apple brought twist in the iPhone X design and now for the lovers of this brand is going to watch a totally new design in their next product which is going to reveal very soon. Apple iPhone X is the speculated to be a gift of their 10th anniversary and it brought some new features and new types of specifications will be revealed in the leaked specs sheet.

Apple's iPhone X is all about the perfection and it seems that it will bring the full screen display that we never saw before in any other predecessor of this renowned brand. Apple iPhone X's design is refreshed and now very small bezels just like the edges of a Samsung. Instead of old fashioned IPS panels now Super AMOLED matrix is used in iPhone X by Apple which they gonna buy from the leading brand Samsung.

Teaser images are indicating that its display will be quite identical to the LG G6 which was the flagship device of LG. Apple X is going to boast 5.8 inch LCD which is going to be a huge display for a smartphone and as you can see that on the 10th anniversary there will be a changed face of Apple iPhone's X which we gonna see.

Chipset is upgraded too and new chip will be called A11 Bionic and it will be using a six core processor to complete all iPhone X's intense processing quite easily. iOS also got some treatment and now iOS 11 will be planted inside to control all the hardware of device and with this software Apple iPhone X is going to obey all the commands passed the user of this gadget.

RAM attached with chip is 3 GB while the internal storage planted is gonna be 64GB and 256GB.

fields.description:
Huawei Honor 10 - Capture The Beauty With Enhanced AI!

After separation Honor is launching 10 as the flagship device which has focused on the AI capabilities of the device. As we all know that from the start it was the subsidiary brand of Huawei but now with Honor 10 they will be called as the separate brand in the market of Pakistan.

Previously both of them have a lot of things in common to jointly take down the Samsung but now Honor's 10 have to fight alone against this beast in smartphone world of Pakistan because they have separated their way for their own good.

Change ways did not cause any changes in Honor 10's specifications and software because still you will get the same feeling that you are using the same old smartphone manufactured by Huawei because Honor did not changed its software for the upcoming 10 and Emotion UI 8 is laid on top of Oreo operating system which is yet the latest product of Google for all the latest devices. As far as the internals of phone are concerned Honor outed 10 with their best equipment available in the market.

All the teaser images have revealed that the next smartphone coming launched by this brand named 10 is going to come with dual camera setup. Notch craze is also seen in this device and 5.84 inch screen of this device is also going to bring the Full Vision display for its users.

Honor 10 has perfected itself with the high end HiSilicon Kirin 970 chipset which is going to power up the display and all other parts of the device. 4 GB of RAM is there to handle the multi-tasking of 10 so keep calm because 4 GB is rated as the good choice in RAM business so it mean that your phone is saved from the trouble caused by RAM.

128 GB of internal storage will keep 10 by Honor spacious and it seems impossible that at some point you will run out of storage at some point. In the last you will get new color option in Honor 10.

fields.description:
Samsung Galaxy Note 8 - The Next Big Thing!

Samsung has decided to continue Galaxy Note series and this time it's 8 which is rising from the ashes of its discontinued sibling. Sometimes things go wrong and we did not get the same results as we expected. The Korean giant is leaving behind all its bad memories and Samsung Galaxy Note 8 is going to launch soon.

It will be a fresh start for company after discontinuation of its most cherished phone. All discontinuation rumors died after launch of Samsung's Galaxy Note 8 and we will see that one day it will be praised as the top ranking phone of the year 2017. No matter what happened in past the upcoming device is equipped with 6.3 inches display.

Samsung Galaxy Note's display has packed super AMOLED technology to make things looks great and sharp from each and every angle. Per inch pixel density of Galaxy Note 8 by Samsung is 522 pixels which is the highest amount yet recorded in the history of smartphone.

Its Resolution is also touching the heights where you will get the highest number which is 1440 x 2960 pixel resolution. Note 8 is protected with corning gorilla glass 5 while it is also dust proof and waterproof because it is IP68 certified to make sure that your device will stay in the water for up to 30 minutes.

Galaxy Note 8 is really a wonder because this phone is the combo of all high-end technical specification to take the company to the new heights. Now you will get the Samsung Galaxy's Note 8 in two different variants where one is coming with 6 GB RAM and 64 GB ROM while the second variant has 128 GB built-in storage.

Samsung Note 8 has dual 12 MP eye on its back which is equipped with high-end techs while on front 8 MP camera is installed for sharp and vibrant selfies.

fields.description:
Samsung Galaxy S8 Plus - Rivals Should Fear The Presence Of Giant!

Samsung is messing things and S8 just appeared again with its Plus version to make sure that both siblings will appear at same time and leave no room for its rival to interfere in their peaceful launch.

It seems that bad days are over and Samsung Galaxy S8 Plus will make it sure that Korean giant will once again hit the milestone that will clear the name of brand and it will help the products like the upcoming Samsung's Galaxy S8 Plus to place in top rankings for long time period.

After little introduction it is time discuss about technical specifications. First of all it is time to meet with Samsung Galaxy S8's Super AMOLED display which is packed inside 6.2 inches LCD while on the top a capacitive touchscreen is embedded that let you enjoy firm touch while playing or doing work.

Galaxy S8 Plus by Samsung is IP68 certified device which means that it is totally dust proof and it also stay in water for up to 30 minutes in case of emergency. Corning gorilla glass is installed on front and back of S8 Plus that also protect it form scratches and smudge.

Touch Wiz UI is embedded on top of android OS v.70 Nougat to give original looks of brand to its users. Samsung S8 Plus has packed the Exynos 8895 Octa chipset which is the highest number available in market while an octa core processor is divided in to two separate groups to reap the maximum power.

Samsung Galaxy's S8 Plus has also avail the services of Adreno 540 to maximize graphical output while playing heavy games. 12 MP camera is attached to back while 8 MP is provided to Galaxy S8 Plus for outstanding selfie result.
